signed to reduce the\nnoise caused by image deconvolution while removing the aberrations caused by\nthe HREW. The computed PSF via phase diversity significantly reduces the\ndegradation caused by the HREW in the near-perihelion HRT data. In addition,\nthe aberration correction increases the noise by a factor of only $1.45$\ncompared to the factor of $3$ increase that results from the usual PD\nreconstructions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 May 2023 20:15:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-02"}
