laneous spin correlations. Our work\nopens the door to understanding surprising connections between many-body scars\nand quantum criticality in systems with a higher value of spin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Jun 2023 14:00:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-02"}
