d the presence of additional low mobility bands, are addressed.\nThe results outlined here provide a concise picture on the bulk conducting\nstates in flux-grown Bi2Se3 single crystals, enabling better control of the\nstructural defects and electronic properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Jun 2023 15:48:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-02"}
